  "description": "A close-up, symmetrical photograph showcases the interior of a vibrant red and white tulip. The petals curl inwards, creating a funnel-like shape that draws the eye towards the flower's center. The innermost petals are a creamy white, transitioning to a striking red at the edges. Prominent black anthers surround a bright yellow stigma, creating a strong contrast. The background is blurred and dark green, suggesting foliage, but the focus is entirely on the intricate details of the tulip's reproductive parts. The lighting is soft, highlighting the textures of the petals and the delicate structure of the flower.",
